<section id="challenge" class="reveal">
  <div class="sec-tag">The Problem</div>
  <div class="sec-num">1.0</div>
  <h2 class="sec-title">The Crisis of Attention</h2>
  <blockquote class="big-quote reveal">"In the modern cockpit, screens are competing for attention, not supporting intention."</blockquote>
  <p class="challenge-desc reveal">As vehicles transition from <strong>mechanical tools to digital hubs</strong>, drivers face an unprecedented crisis of Cognitive Overload. Traditional navigation systems are "demanding" — they require active interpretation of complex 2D maps, constant voice interruptions, and manual input. This fragmentation of attention disconnects the driver from the road.</p>
  <div class="challenge-grid reveal">
    <div class="challenge-card">
      <div class="ccard-num">CHALLENGE 01</div>
      <div class="ccard-title">The "Screenification" Problem</div>
      <p class="ccard-body">Modern vehicles force constant focus-switching between road and screen, causing cognitive overload and fragmented attention.</p>
      <div class="ccard-stat">40<span style="font-size:16px">%</span></div>
      <div class="ccard-stat-label">Increase in reaction time</div>
    </div>
    <div class="challenge-card">
      <div class="ccard-num">CHALLENGE 02</div>
      <div class="ccard-title">The "Disconnected" Driver</div>
